des:
If you are in Christ, this skill will encourage you. You will hear who God says you are according to His word. Scriptural reference is provided with each phrase. This skill list is based on the work of author Henry Blackaby and his book "Experiencing God." 

The grace of the Lord Jesus Christ, and the love of God, and the fellowship of the Holy Spirit, be with you all. - 2 Cor 13:14 (NASB)
